Class VCS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cisco.dvbu.ps.deploytool.gui.core.module.vcs.VCS

  • public class VCS
extends java.lang.Object

    Bean object for VCS module VCS records. Intended to be serialized/deserialized by Jackson into/from JSON.

    1.0
